features: BALANCE-N-BRIGHTEN COLOR CORRECTING POWDER FOUNDATION: This award-winning foundation handmade in Italy is made up of pressed powders to help you create a perfect canvas and a natural, demi-matte finish. Build your ideal coverage without worrying about caking—this favorite feels weightless and looks flawless.
SAND: Get this award-winning powder foundation in the perfect shade for deep olive skin with golden undertones.

SELF-ADJUSTS TO MATCH YOUR SKIN TONE: Treat yourself to a baked powder foundation that nourishes as it perfects. This natural demi-matte formula gives you creamy coverage that's packed with antioxidants Centella Asiatica and White Tea Extracts for soothing hydration all day long

PERFECT FOR : This one's a crowd-pleaser. Perfect for even mature skin, uneven complexions, and those with fine lines and wrinkles, the light and airy baked powder foundation gives you a flawless face without feeling (or looking) cakey and heavy, no matter your skin type.
HOW TO APPLY: Swirl your brush in the foundation powder. Then, stroke on your face, blending outward and upward. Repeat to build coverage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy and fast to apply
reviews.reviewText: I just love this product! U don’t need foundation, this stuff is like magic. Hides all my “mature skin” and feels like i don’t have anything on. Covers so nicely but also looks natural, not like I’m trying too hard. I’ve got 4 kids and little time to make my face look somewhat awake, so this is fast, easy, and makes me feel good. That’s what’s it all about right! Repeat customer on this one for sure! I also dropped it by accident yesterday and it didn’t break or crumble!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gentle, sheer, coverage
reviews.reviewText: I love this foundation. Glazes over my skin and doesn't feel plastic-y, heavy, or 'dried on'. It's enough coverage to look soft and smooth without looking painted or fake. I use a little mascara and a wee bit of blush, shiny chapstick, and I'm ready to go. I still look like a grandma, but a grandma with balanced skin and a bright smile. I will add that in the summer, I used the next-to-lightest color and it fit perfectly, but as the sunshine left my skin, I had to move to the lightest shade in order to feel as if the tint matches my skin tone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great natural looking makeup
reviews.reviewText: I normally wear Estee Lauder double-wear powder makeup. I was searching for a less expensive alternative. This is a good alternative for a sheer, but somewhat buildable coverage makeup. It is not as opaque as the doublewear, nor does it have the same stay in place ability over time. BUT it is a great alternative for a light, everyday makeup. I don't find it drying, but I do use moisturizer. I don't find that it falls into my fine lines and wrinkles as much as different brands of the same type of makeup. Also, I find it very hard to match my color in almost all brands except Estee, but this one does! I wear this pretty much every day. The real test will come in the humid summer months. Something else to add, for those like myself, I find that most powder makeups make my face itch, this one does not. For the price, I think it's a great makeup.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WOW. JUST WOW. 4.5 out of 5; minus a little for no color/shade samples
reviews.reviewText: I'm almost 60/F, some wrinkles and a fair amount of discoloration, red spots, and sun damage, esp. on cheeks.This foundation (baked balance and brighten, color FAIR) is really easy to use. Feels like nothing, even when building. I used only basic, soft, fluffy brushes I had on hand; they worked well for light coverage, but I do think a denser brush option - like a retracting kabuki, as recommended - might work better for building.Very good coverage on bare skin (moisturizar only), pracrically perfect over an inexpensive primer. Almost all my flaws disappeared, even without concealer.Did not settle in wrinkles, either. I FEEL PRET-TY, OH-SO PRET-TY!...or, at least, "not bad for an old broad, not at all!".I do find that using primer is better over large pores and significant discoloration, such as have I. I used a budget brand with spf 30 and the foundation went on perfectly.It's FAST, too. The longest part if the process is waiting for the primer to dry, maybe 1-3 minutes.Found it difficult to shade match - but to be fair: When is it *not* difficult?Would be a very nice thing if Laura Geller Beauty offered an inexpensive "sampler" (say, $5.00 for just enough product for 1/2 face in two adjacent shades) to help in this process.I tried "PORCELAIN" first, but it was just a tad too light. The model wearing "FAIR" looks like an olive tone to me, whereas (I think?) I'm more peachy, like the "LIGHT" model - but I'm super pale...but ... but.. hem ..haw..Seems really wasteful to open, use once and return a full product to try a color that isn't quite right, as I have. "Samplers" would really help reduce the volume of product returns, not to mention reduce waste and carbon footprints - just sayin'.Step up,😀Laura Geller. Make the planet as beautiful as you have me!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Believe the reviews, it is orangey
reviews.reviewText: I bought this because I love powder foundations. I’m always on the hunt for kinds that look the most like natural skin when applied. I also use MAC Studio Fix Powder Foundation, which is fine but slightly heavy to me. I thought I’d give this one a try since it supposed to be slightly glowy. There were plenty of reviewers that said that it looked orangey on their skin or was too dark. I ordered a shade lighter than I would have otherwise, due to these comments. However the product did turn out a bit orangey on me. Luckily, I can combine it with my MAC foundation, which is slightly too light, and it turns out ok. But I wouldn’t wear it on its own.My all-time fave powder foundation is sadly mostly sold in Germany so it’s tough to get here, but Amazon sometimes sells it - Art Deco Hydra Mineral Foundation. If you order it from Amazon, it comes from Germany and the packaging for shipping is hit or miss so it may arrive broken. I use a combination of shades 65 and 70.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works well and covers naturally
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this makeup. It feels and looks so natural. Not at all heavy or flaky. I have some fine lines around my eye area and was afraid that it would enhance them but it didn’t! Looks amazing throughout the day! Would recommend to all skin types and ages

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The Best Powder Foundation
reviews.reviewText: For over 25 years I used a compact with a powder puff, mostly Clinque, and others. I had myself talked into thinking I would never like applying powder with a brush, but after reading the 5 star reviews of this one I tried it. Now I LOVE it. As I am applying it I can actually see my skin tone even out. It doesn't cause my sensitive skin to break out or get oily. I love being able to control the coverage as well. I go all day without reapplying and when I wash my face before bed I see the powder foundation on my washcloth, it is still in place. Awesome! I also love that it marketed to mature women as well.
One of the nicest foundations I have ever used. Good coverage and light weight. Doesn’t feel like I’m wearing makeup.
El producto es lo que esperaba y el vendedor se esmeró en solucionar el problema que hubo. Muchas gracias

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Was a little sceptical but this is my new foundation I am almost 60 and it looks very good, no clogging in wrinkles and very light but great coverage I am very impressed
Kenne dieses Produkt schon lange, bin sehr zufrieden, für mich der beste Puder, Lieferung ging schnell. Gerne wieder.
Ich benutze es seit Jahren und ist nach wie vor das beste auf dem Markt. Ich liebe diese foundation.
